name: Go Car
description:
GO FAST, DON’T CRASH!
Speed cars up, slow them down, turn left and right, keep them from colliding and going BOOM!

Send all the cars into the correct garages like a boss, in this retro styled 8-Bit traffic management puzzler.

Speed cars up, slow them down, turn left and right, keep them from colliding and going BOOM!

Many have failed, will you make it to the end?
GO GO GO CAR!
_____________________________________
Features:
- 60 unique and challenging levels
- 2 areas, with more on the way
- 80's styled retro graphics
- Chip tune music and sound effects
_____________________________________
